172410,"uid":158899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c0609d53f7b35cdc2b54bdb9b205f3213db7fba","tid":2172410,"uid":369320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T15:17:03.000Z","msg":"點解你同我經歷咁似<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T15:28:59.000Z","msg":"點解會有第二個我 你講下你係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T16:11:57.000Z","msg":"我小學比個屎忽miss罰小食時間去佢個位罰企，食飯坐佢隔離0自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日吼我唔識個啲嘢嚟問我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又改我花名又話我精神分裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T16:19:16.000Z","msg":"小6個時 轉左條女 做班主任 教我英文<br />\n一星期一次 默書 我次次0-20分<br />\n一星期一次食飯時間叫我企佢隔黎讀英文 次次一個鍾食飯得番半個鐘<br />\n有次我喊撚左 佢仲叫我唔好企禁近 話驚我啲眼淚滴到佢個飯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好記得個次 佢食緊 青豆 咸魚 飯 個死老野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鐵飯盒 粉紅色筷子<br />\n又矮 小學已經矮過我 你老味"},{"pid":"f84a96f6516958d78c794daaabf292b806828693","tid":2172410,"uid":71632,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T16:34:13.000Z","msg":"大波女教師幫我打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83014349d4b274a5898bb259ce9745b64d92a270","tid":2172410,"uid":169341,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T16:37:33.000Z","msg":"我畫畫廢到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小學個仆街miss將我份功課貼堂貼足一個學期搞到我成日俾人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />條撚樣早幾年好似俾人炒撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />抵撚死啦屌你老母臭閪"},{"pid":"aeeebee04a5892546cf65ffda262a6f29625551b","tid":2172410,"uid":21141,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T16:44:39.000Z","msg":"小學個陣唔記得做乜要去隔離班房上堂<br />\n跟返原本個班既座位咁坐返低<br />\n上完之後隔離班我坐完個位個女同學話唔見左銀包跟著同老師講<br />\n之後兩個班既班主任同訓導主任二話不說捉我出來盤我話做乜偷人野，我大大聲話冇偷過，佢地唔撚信認定係我，係全班面前屌㭍我，仲話我偷完野仲咁理直氣壯，身為一個人好無恥，鬧撚到我喊，後尾查到係隔離班某條撚樣偷既就不了了之，我屌你老母，簡直童年陰影，記一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a40f7996831dc346c743bc4cf81a9b6706f3ee77","tid":2172410,"uid":357081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"69e832031515772a89aaf99ac797ed74adb04783","tid":2172410,"uid":130466,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"9b4a51dd0fa20b226f1f9749441654cc4d552b5e","tid":2172410,"uid":369320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T14:51:01.000Z","msg":"我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n十幾年前小學老師好仆街，唔記得帶書同無交功課就倒哂你櫃桶啲嘢落街，又用本書車鳩個自閉同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最尾個同學搭校巴返學喊到仆街，仲要唔敢返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個同學一定有心理陰影"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T15:03:00.000Z","msg":"成班八婆係到吹水，咁我諗住放低本簿就走，點知佢突然停低講：你叫我地早晨啦<br />\n<br />\n我講完仲成班成到恥笑我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢條八婆後來車禍死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T16:50:06.000Z","msg":"karma"},{"pid":"01bf8a32be95675dc0681f9e04eef6290782e943","tid":2172410,"uid":342036,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:04:50.000Z","msg":"有年冬天嘅月份但仲未換冬季校服，然後聽到隔離精英班教中文嘅女老師（訓導老師嚟），話可以著校褸（姐係可以夏季校服加校褸），我信咗佢講。<br />\n<br />\n第二日，我就係夏季校服加校褸咁返學，門口有個訓導男老師，叫停我，然後話做咩著校褸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我話我覺得凍。佢就up一大輪話我態度差，話咩「人地講咩就做咩，人地做賊你就可以做賊？」「你讀書讀上腦？」<br />\n<br />\n然後，嬲得濟叫屋企人投訴個男訓導老師態度惡劣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後個男訓導俾人照肺兼謝晒皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />從此佢無再喺學校作惡"},{"pid":"1b9760a10120abab18de185be9661b98eadf096d","tid":2172410,"uid":121947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:09:24.000Z","msg":"小學有個同學俾個呀sir掉書包出課室,啲書飛到一地都係,然後當佢狗咁鬧,叫佢掹住耳仔行出去執返啲書再喺課室門口罰企<br />\n過左廿幾年都仲好記得<br />\n青衣某小學劉x濤老師"},{"pid":"03f83b8c7ca2d408834aeb22d8b826f8bebe9ada","tid":2172410,"uid":44083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:59:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d22ed858a9d3d96d8efb27f2f9fff04b14c38bf3","tid":2172410,"uid":265817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T18:15:33.000Z","msg":"有個暴力傾向既訓導留人堂留到夜晚11點半"},{"pid":"a7f3b6a322396e0b066f52d9339b993af1744c49","tid":2172410,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T19:16:26.000Z","msg":"老師走廊差錯腳仆街"},{"pid":"809d82f678dc84d63525a78f248ac26a13c09149","tid":2172410,"uid":188907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94ca1bb4df121dccc2a1bc45f939ef7c10f5ecf5","tid":2172410,"uid":290762,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T15:13:19.000Z","msg":"試過無啦啦沒收咗我部psp（個時上堂無打，係小息同lunch同人組隊打芒亨），然後部機比人偷咗，第二日同我講如果我嚟緊考試成績去到頭幾名就賠返比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T19:23:13.000Z","msg":"On9佢自己賣撚左咋掛<br />\n最後點？"},{"pid":"65b21bfe6f2ba5c1a528f1a0fc5f848f5bc1241d","tid":2172410,"uid":232580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T19:23:44.000Z","msg":"中一唔知點解比個班主任針<br />\n次次調位都坐最尾<br />\n仲要揾個1米8嘅大肥仔坐我前面擋住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（我係排幾前下嘅女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n細個個陣唔知點解<br />\n大個左覺得係針<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我真係無做過乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後尾升中二好開心可以脫離呢個仆街<br />\n點知又係佢做班主任<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果調位又係習慣性擺我去後面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}